# Native Homebrew bundle. This is now a PARTIAL Brewfile: plain homebrew/core
# CLI formulae were migrated to mise's experimental brew bootstrap and live in
# config/mise/config.toml under [bootstrap.packages] (installed by
# `dfm install mise` via `mise bootstrap packages apply`).
#
# What stays here on native brew, on purpose:
#   - casks (mise brew-cask is experimental, no import/prune)
#   - imagemagick, ffmpeg, coreutils (GNU) and their linked dependency closure
#   - yabai/skhd (codesign + sudo installs mise's shim doesn't cover)
# PHP is no longer managed here — phpenv.fish (homebrew provider) owns it.
# Applied with `dfm brew install` (brew bundle). Do not re-add the migrated
# formulae here — mise resolves their dependency closure automatically.
